data.description:
Beautifully renovated 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom PLUS Bonus Room home situated in a central location just a 15 min drive to the All American Gate of Fort Liberty. Bonus Room has separate heating and cooling unit. Dual Zone. Roof 2023. HVAC 2023. Hot Water Tank 2020. Garbage disposal 2023. Newer appliances. New Fixtures and hardware. Updated front landscaping with freshly painted covered front porch and shutters. .20 acre lot. Privacy fenced back yard. Bonus room has a walk in/storage closet. New plank flooring through out Living room and bedrooms. Carpeted stairway leading to plank floor above garage bonus room. Newly installed Master bathroom and guest bathroom flooring. Brand new kitchen and dining room flooring. Come check out this home! It will not last. Custom designed with modern touches! Move in ready. Just unpack! 
Still under minor updates/construction. Please mind our dust.
